  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, he had been arrested-- he was in a smaller town about 50 miles east of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was much worse there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was arrested and brought to Sachsenhausen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he came and he was released.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He came to us, I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with no hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, uh, what they did to the clothes, the regular clothes, I guess they disinfect them, and looked dreadful, all wrinkled and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew him distinctly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, the teachers that came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think even then, the most, uh, people who doubted it, finally realized if that is possible in an orderly state.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In some way, perhaps it was still encouraging that the population as such didn't participate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then they couldn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think there was a bigger surprise, actually, that the population didn't go run around applauding, you see.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Perhaps some did, but what my personal experience, not at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
